<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/status-bar.css">
  <style>
    .service-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }
    .service-card {
      border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-color, #4a9eff);
      padding-left: 1rem;
    }
    .service-card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .service-card p {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .service-card ul {
      margin: 0.75rem 0 0 0;
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .service-card ul li {
      margin: 0.25rem 0;
    }
    .service-links {
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .service-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      opacity: 0.85;
    }
    .service-links a:hover {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', { user: user, character: character }) %>

  <main class="container">
    <h1>Application Infrastructure</h1>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Production-ready network of specialized services for automation, real-time collaboration, and distributed computing.</p>

    <div class="service-grid">

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Conversational AI Engine</h3>
        <p>Production Claude API integration with stateful conversation management, voice synthesis, and enterprise token metering.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Anthropic Sonnet 4+ streaming responses</li>
          <li>Persistent multi-session state</li>
          <li>WebRTC voice input/output</li>
          <li>Token consumption analytics</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Distributed MMO Framework</h3>
        <p>WebGL-rendered persistent universe with player-generated content, democratic asset governance, and cross-instance state synchronization.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Three.js spatial navigation engine</li>
          <li>Community asset voting protocol</li>
          <li>Parametric talent progression</li>
          <li>Server mesh handoff system</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="service-links">
          <a href="/auth">Sign in to play â†’</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Algorithmic Trading Engine</h3>
        <p>Multi-strategy execution platform for cryptocurrency markets with position sizing, rebalancing logic, and performance attribution.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>CEX API aggregation layer</li>
          <li>DCA/Grid/Momentum strategies</li>
          <li>Real-time P&L calculation</li>
          <li>Multi-asset support (10+ pairs)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Geospatial Engagement Platform</h3>
        <p>Location-based gamification system with proximity detection, achievement mechanics, and virtual economy for physical businesses.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>GPS check-in verification</li>
          <li>Progressive badge unlocks</li>
          <li>Competitive ranking system</li>
          <li>Redemption marketplace</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Omnichannel Payment Processor</h3>
        <p>Abstraction layer for traditional and blockchain payment rails with dynamic address generation and transparent fee calculation.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Fiat: Stripe, PayPal, Venmo, Zelle</li>
          <li>Crypto: BTC, ETH, USDC, SOL, LTC</li>
          <li>On-demand QR encoding</li>
          <li>Transaction fee passthrough</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Content Aggregation Pipeline</h3>
        <p>Automated extraction and normalization of web content with sentiment analysis, categorization, and social engagement layer.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Multi-domain scraping orchestration</li>
          <li>NLP-based categorization</li>
          <li>Threaded comment system</li>
          <li>User interaction metrics</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Service Orchestration Dashboard</h3>
        <p>Unified control plane for distributed microservice mesh with telemetry streaming, process management, and alert routing.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>12-service health monitoring</li>
          <li>Real-time log aggregation</li>
          <li>Process lifecycle controls</li>
          <li>CPU/Memory/Network metrics</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>WebGL Rendering Pipeline</h3>
        <p>GPU-accelerated 3D scene composition with Blender interop, skeletal animation, and real-time lighting for browser environments.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Three.js renderer abstraction</li>
          <li>Blender model import pipeline</li>
          <li>User-controlled camera systems</li>
          <li>Frame-synced animation loops</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Portfolio CMS</h3>
        <p>Project documentation and media management system for client deliverables with responsive gallery rendering and metadata tagging.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Grid-based gallery layouts</li>
          <li>Project case studies</li>
          <li>Asset organization & search</li>
          <li>Mobile-optimized views</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>QR Code Generator API</h3>
        <p>REST endpoint for programmatic QR generation with vector/raster export, error correction tuning, and embedded analytics pixels.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>PNG/SVG format support</li>
          <li>Parameterized sizing/styling</li>
          <li>Batch generation endpoints</li>
          <li>Scan tracking hooks</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
  <script src="/javascripts/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
